  <entry>
    <title></title>
    <link href="/2023/03/19/%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/"/>
    <url>/2023/03/19/%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="基本数据结构与基本输入输出"><a href="#基本数据结构与基本输入输出" class="headerlink" title="基本数据结构与基本输入输出"></a>基本数据结构与基本输入输出</h1><hr><h2 id="简单输入输出与基本概念"><a href="#简单输入输出与基本概念" class="headerlink" title="简单输入输出与基本概念"></a>简单输入输出与基本概念</h2><h2 id="python是一门脚本语言-他又一些很方便的特点"><a href="#python是一门脚本语言-他又一些很方便的特点" class="headerlink" title="python是一门脚本语言,他又一些很方便的特点"></a>python是一门脚本语言,他又一些很方便的特点<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment">#在‘#’后面的是注释</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;撒打发士大夫&quot;</span>) <span class="hljs-comment">#在&quot;&quot;内的是字符串你可以在终端输出你想说的</span><br>a=<span class="hljs-built_in">eval</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">input</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请输入&quot;</span>))<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(a) <span class="hljs-comment">#python对变量的输出处理的很好,很方便</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#去试试下面这段代码输入sin(23)</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> math <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">eval</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">input</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请输入:&quot;</span>)))<br><span class="hljs-comment">#猜猜这个eval函数干了什么</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></h2><h2 id="函数"><a href="#函数" class="headerlink" title="函数"></a>函数</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">fun</span>(<span class="hljs-params">a,b</span>):<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>(a+b)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span>():<br>a=fun(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">4</span>)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__==<span class="hljs-string">&quot;__main__&quot;</span>:<br>main()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="库-pip"><a href="#库-pip" class="headerlink" title="库 pip"></a>库 pip</h2><pre><code class="hljs">简单来形容,库就是别人已经写好的一堆函数与对象,你可以来用turtlenumpymatplot</code></pre><hr><h2 id="变量"><a href="#变量" class="headerlink" title="变量"></a>变量</h2><h2 id="他不需要声明变量你可以直接-他会自己判断"><a href="#他不需要声明变量你可以直接-他会自己判断" class="headerlink" title="他不需要声明变量你可以直接,他会自己判断"></a>他不需要声明变量你可以直接,他会自己判断<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">a=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;大师傅&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#字符串 </span><br>b=<span class="hljs-number">34.5</span><br>我是变量=<span class="hljs-number">4</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#在python里中文也可以成为一种变量</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(我是变量)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></h2><h2 id="数组"><a href="#数组" class="headerlink" title="数组"></a>数组</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">c=(<span class="hljs-number">23</span>,<span class="hljs-number">34</span>,<span class="hljs-number">65.43</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;asdfs&quot;</span>) <br><span class="hljs-comment">#被()包含在内用分号隔开,被称为元组,里面可以是任何东西,元组是不能修改的</span><br>d=[<span class="hljs-number">23</span>,<span class="hljs-number">34</span>,<span class="hljs-number">65.43</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;asdfs&quot;</span>]<br><span class="hljs-comment">#被[]包括的,里面的可以修改,也可以添加与减少</span><br>朱铭扬=&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;名字&#x27;</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;朱铭扬&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;性别&#x27;</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;男&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;职业&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&quot;学生&quot;</span>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">#被&#123;&#125;包含的是字典,&#x27;:&#x27;前的叫键,&#x27;:后的叫值</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(c[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]) <span class="hljs-comment">#你可以通过[]内的索引来得到他们,从零开始</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(c[-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]) <span class="hljs-comment">#负索引意味着你可以从右往左来访问他们 </span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(朱铭扬.keys())<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(朱铭扬[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;性别&#x27;</span>])<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="字符串"><a href="#字符串" class="headerlink" title="字符串"></a>字符串</h3><p>字符串是一个很重要的类型</p><hr><h2 id="控制结构"><a href="#控制结构" class="headerlink" title="控制结构"></a>控制结构</h2><h3 id="if-…elif"><a href="#if-…elif" class="headerlink" title="if …elif"></a>if …elif</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>):<span class="hljs-comment">#为1时继续</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">elif</span>(符合什么条件)<br><span class="hljs-comment">#一句画循环</span><br>-n <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> n &lt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> n<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="循环"><a href="#循环" class="headerlink" title="循环"></a>循环</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment">### for</span><br>```python<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>（<span class="hljs-number">2</span>，<span class="hljs-number">6</span>）：<br>do something<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>):<br><span class="hljs-comment">#一句话循环</span><br>n = <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">input</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Please enter a positive integer: &quot;</span>))<br><br>factors = [x <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> x <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, n + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> n % x == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>]<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Factors of&quot;</span>, n, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;:&quot;</span>, factors)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># python批量更换后缀名</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> os<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 列出当前目录下所有的文件</span><br>files = os.listdir(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> filename <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> files:<br>portion = os.path.splitext(filename)<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 如果后缀是.dat</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> portion[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] == <span class="hljs-string">&quot;.dat&quot;</span>:  <br><span class="hljs-comment"># 重新组合文件名和后缀名</span><br>newname = portion[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;.txt&quot;</span>   <br>os.rename(filename,newnam<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#原文链接：https://blog.csdn.net/rosefun96/article/details/78968490</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="try…except…finally"><a href="#try…except…finally" class="headerlink" title="try…except…finally"></a>try…except…finally</h3><h2 id="with…"><a href="#with…" class="headerlink" title="with…."></a>with….</h2><hr><h3 id="一些可以去做的练习"><a href="#一些可以去做的练习" class="headerlink" title="一些可以去做的练习"></a>一些可以去做的练习</h3><p>可以去试一下turtle:画动的蟒蛇,画五角星<br>我的脑洞:可以利用极限的定义来计算$\frac{sin(0)}{0}$</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
